text: Kerry Owen (born 23 June 1943) is an Australian cricketer. He played one first-class match for New South Wales in 1965/66. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1943 births Category:Living people Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney
